Actually, with that interface the implementation could be as simple as:

```py
class Factory(object):

    def __init__(self, schema, defaults={}):
        self.schema = schema
        self.defaults = defaults

    def dump(self, data):
        complete_data = {}
        complete_data.update(self.defaults)
        complete_data.update(data)
        return self.schema.dump(complete_data)
```

